flowchart LR
%% view: VIEW-CONTAINER (container)
N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API["Checkout API"]:::container
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE["Payment Engine"]:::container
N_CONT_RISK_SCORER["Risk Scorer"]:::container
N_EXT_BANK_GW[["Bank Gateway"]]:::external
N_ACT_SUPPORT(("Support Agent")):::person
N_SYS_PAYMENTS["Payments System"]:::system
N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API -->|depends_on: Delegates payment authorization. catalog: payment authorization is requested, checkout is active| N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE
N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API -->|part_of| N_SYS_PAYMENTS
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Sends high-risk review notification. catalog: support agent is notified, payment review is pending, support agent| N_ACT_SUPPORT
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Returns decline outcome for customer messaging. catalog: payment is declined, decline reason| N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Returns temporary unavailable response when bank link is down. catalog: bank link is unavailable| N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Requests fraud scoring. catalog: fraud check is enabled, risk score is high, risk score| N_CONT_RISK_SCORER
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Calls bank authorization API. catalog: bank link is available, payment authorization is requested| N_EXT_BANK_GW
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|part_of| N_SYS_PAYMENTS

